creator: Dil Mil Inc.
descriptionHtml:
** FEATURED BY FORBES, TECHCRUNCH & MORE**

One relationship per hour & one marriage per day reported to Dil Mil. With over 10 million matches made Dil Mil is the leading South Asian dating app that is completely free to use.

Dil Mil has over TWO MILLION users in the US, UK, AU or Canada identifying with diverse communities such as Gujarati, Punjabi, Sindhi, Bengali, Tamil, Telugu, Malayali, Maharashtrian, Kannada, and Rajasthani.

Date easy knowing that we ensure a real, high-quality community. Photo and data privacy, hands-on support, ethnicity/community filters, and advanced matching algorithms have helped form countless high quality matches. Facebook or phone number sign-in verifies real profiles and enhances security.

Swipe right on someone you like. If they like you back you will match and get to talk to each other for free. You can use in-app upgrades to match with more South Asian singles faster.

Dil Mil has been featured in: Forbes, TechCrunch, Wall Street Journal, India Times, YourStory and more!

Sign up for free and start searching for your perfect match!

---------------------------------

SUPPORT: For in-app chat support visit your Account screen > click on top right Settings icon > scroll down to Help & Support. Alternatively, you can email us: support@dilmil.co.

We do a lot of cool things for Dil Mil couples. To submit a success story please email: success@dilmil.co

Privacy Policy: https://dilmil.co/privacy-policy/
Terms of Use: https://dilmil.co/terms-of-use/

---------------------------------

You can unlock premium features by subscribing to VIP Elite:

VIP Elite gives you access to all of the premium features such as Instant Matches (see who likes you already), Boosts (be the top profile on Dil Mil), Unlimited Likes, Notes (directly message potential matches), Change Location (swipe from anywhere), Rewind (change your previous decision), and Reset Dislikes (undo all previous dislikes) by optionally purchasing VIP Elite starting at $34.99 per month.

Once you're VIP Elite, you can also purchase additional Boosts via an a la carte purchase screen starting at $5.99.

If you choose to purchase VIP Elite, payment will be charged to your iTunes Account, and your account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period. Auto-renewal may be turned off at any time by going to your iTunes Account Settings after purchase. No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during the active subscription period.

Happy Dil Miling!

One relationship per hour & one marriage per day reported to Dil Mil. With over 20 million matches made Dil Mil is the leading South Asian dating app that is completely free to use.

Dil Mil has over TWO MILLION users in the US, UK, AU or Canada identifying with diverse communities such as Gujarati, Punjabi, Sindhi, Bengali, Tamil, Telugu, Malayali, Maharashtrian, Kannada, and Rajasthani.

Date easy knowing that we ensure a real, high-quality community. Photo and data privacy, hands-on support, ethnicity/community filters, and advanced matching algorithms have helped form countless high quality matches. Facebook or phone number sign-in verifies real profiles and enhances security.

Sign up for free and start searching for your perfect match!

---------------------------------

Once you're VIP Elite, you can also purchase additional Boosts via an a la carte purchase screen starting at $5.99.

If you choose to purchase VIP Elite, payment will be charged to your iTunes Account, and your account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period. Happy Dil Miling!
